  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Lead the Invasion. Conquer the Galaxy. Learn from Your Mistakes. (Or Don't.)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zyx empire is rising again! Now, it's your job to invade planets, harvest resources, and strategically obliterate any species standing in your way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Outsmart your enemies by predicting their next move!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616580/extras/26c3ca8cb03bca4530c7f05fde5506e0.poster.avif?t=1753565983\" width=760 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616580/extras/26c3ca8cb03bca4530c7f05fde5506e0.webm?t=1753565983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616580/extras/26c3ca8cb03bca4530c7f05fde5506e0.mp4?t=1753565983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each mission drops you into enemy territory. Your job? <strong>Land, scout, extract resources, and analyze enemy behavior</strong> - all while staying alive for 20 turns <i>or</i> ensuring the opposition doesn’t.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build infrastructure during missions!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616580/extras/ec416588389e7d441790dcf5c5c24475.poster.avif?t=1753565983\" width=774 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616580/extras/ec416588389e7d441790dcf5c5c24475.webm?t=1753565983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616580/extras/ec416588389e7d441790dcf5c5c24475.mp4?t=1753565983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 missions (12 procedurally generated, 3 boss fights). Plus, there are occasional extra missions on normal and hard difficulties.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 difficulty levels - hard mode unlocks after completing normal.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ enemy unit types, each with 4 variants that scale in strength. Stronger enemies appear on hard difficulty.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mix of tower defense and turn-based strategy. Build turrets, extract minerals, and fight off waves of enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ironman Mode only. Every decision counts. No take-backs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique combat mechanics. Predict enemy movement - you don’t shoot <i>at</i> them, you shoot where they <i>will be</i>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Lead the Invasion. Conquer the Galaxy. Learn from Your Mistakes. (Or Don't.)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zyx empire is rising again! Now, it's your job to invade planets, harvest resources, and strategically obliterate any species standing in your way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Outsmart your enemies by predicting their next move!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616580/extras/26c3ca8cb03bca4530c7f05fde5506e0.poster.avif?t=1753565983\" width=760 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616580/extras/26c3ca8cb03bca4530c7f05fde5506e0.webm?t=1753565983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616580/extras/26c3ca8cb03bca4530c7f05fde5506e0.mp4?t=1753565983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each mission drops you into enemy territory. Your job? <strong>Land, scout, extract resources, and analyze enemy behavior</strong> - all while staying alive for 20 turns <i>or</i> ensuring the opposition doesn’t.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build infrastructure during missions!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616580/extras/ec416588389e7d441790dcf5c5c24475.poster.avif?t=1753565983\" width=774 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616580/extras/ec416588389e7d441790dcf5c5c24475.webm?t=1753565983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3616580/extras/ec416588389e7d441790dcf5c5c24475.mp4?t=1753565983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 missions (12 procedurally generated, 3 boss fights). Plus, there are occasional extra missions on normal and hard difficulties.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 difficulty levels - hard mode unlocks after completing normal.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ enemy unit types, each with 4 variants that scale in strength. Stronger enemies appear on hard difficulty.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mix of tower defense and turn-based strategy. Build turrets, extract minerals, and fight off waves of enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ironman Mode only. Every decision counts. No take-backs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique combat mechanics. Predict enemy movement - you don’t shoot <i>at</i> them, you shoot where they <i>will be</i>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
